<div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-sky-500">Careers</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
        Build the future with us
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8">
        We're creating tools that empower businesses, developers, and creators. Join a team that values craftsmanship, innovation, and meaningful impact.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white pb-24 sm:pb-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 text-base/7 text-gray-600">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Why work with us</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          We're a small, focused team building powerful tools for modern businesses. Every feature we ship, every workflow we design, and every line of code we write moves the product forward in meaningful ways.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6">
          You'll work closely with founders, influence product direction, and help shape a platform used by real customers across industries.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">How we work</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          We believe in clarity, craftsmanship, and ownership. We value thoughtful execution over rushed output, and we give our team the space to do their best work.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6">
          Our culture is built on trust, autonomy, and a shared commitment to building something exceptional.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-50 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-sky-500">Our values</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">
        What we stand for
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Craftsmanship</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          We obsess over details and build with intention. Quality is never an afterthought.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Ownership</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Everyone has a voice. Everyone contributes. Everyone shapes the product.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Focus</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          We prioritize what matters and avoid unnecessary complexity or noise.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-sky-500">Open roles</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">
        Join our growing team
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8">
        We’re always looking for talented people. Here are the roles we're currently hiring for.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

      <!-- Role Card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Full-Stack Engineer</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Help build core features, integrations, and scalable systems.
        </p>
        <%= link_to "Apply now", "#",
          class: "mt-6 inline-block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-500 inset-ring-1 inset-ring-sky-200 hover:bg-sky-50" %>
      </div>

      <!-- Role Card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Product Designer</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Shape the user experience and visual identity of our platform.
        </p>
        <%= link_to "Apply now", "#",
          class: "mt-6 inline-block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-500 inset-ring-1 inset-ring-sky-200 hover:bg-sky-50" %>
      </div>

      <!-- Role Card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Customer Success Lead</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Work directly with customers to ensure they succeed with our tools.
        </p>
        <%= link_to "Apply now", "#",
          class: "mt-6 inline-block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-500 inset-ring-1 inset-ring-sky-200 hover:bg-sky-50" %>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-sky-500 py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl lg:col-span-7">
      Don't see a role that fits? We'd still love to hear from you.
    </h2>

    <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:pt-2">
      <%= link_to "Send us your resume", contact_path,
        class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-500 shadow-xs hover:bg-sky-100 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
